import styled from '@emotion/styled'
import { Container, Grid, Stack, Typography } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'
import BookmarkIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Bookmark';

const ArtWrap = styled('img')(() => ({
    width: "100%",
    borderRadius: 30,
    border: "#6a6a6a",
    borderWidth: 1,
    borderStyle: "solid",
    padding: 10
}))

export default function AssestOverView(props) {
    return (
        <Container>

            <Grid container>
                <Stack pt={10} useFlexGap flexDirection="row" flexWrap="wrap" spacing={5}>
                    <Grid item xs={5}>
                        <ArtWrap alt='art' src={props.src} />
                    </Grid>
                    <Grid item >
                        <Stack>
                            <Typography fontWeight={700} variant='h3'>{props.name}</Typography>
                            <Typography fontWeight={400} variant='body1'>Owned by {props.own}</Typography>
                            <Stack>
                                <Typography fontWeight={400} variant='body1'><BookmarkIcon />{props.type}</Typography>
                            </Stack>
                            <Typography fontWeight={700} variant='h3'>{props.name}</Typography>
                        </Stack>
                    </Grid>
                </Stack>
            </Grid>
        </Container>
    )
}
